{{Infobox power station | name = Brandåa Power Station | name_official = ''Brandåa kraftverk'' | image =Brandåa kraftverk.JPG | location_map = Møre og Romsdal | location_map_caption = Location in [[Møre og Romsdal]] county | coordinates = {{coord|63|05|32|N|9|13|23|E|type:landmark|display=inline,title}} | location = [[Rindal]], [[Møre og Romsdal]] | country = Norway | status = O | construction_began = 2006 | commissioned = {{Start date and age|2009}} | decommissioned = | cost = | owner = Svorka Produksjon<ref name="Kvien">Kvien, Jon-Kåre, & Stian Sørli. 2008. ''Utfordringer med prosjektering av uklassifiserte vassdragsanlegg''. Trondheim: SWECO Norge AS.</ref> | operator = | psps_upper_res = | psps_upper_res_capacity = | psps_penstocks = | psps_lower_res = | psps_lower_res_capacity = | psps_hydraulic_head = 373&nbsp;m | psps_generators = | psps_pumpgenerators = | psps_pumps = | ps_units_operational = | ps_units_manu_model = | ps_units_uc = | ps_units_planned = | ps_units_cancelled = | ps_units_decommissioned= | ps_electrical_capacity = 4.1 | ps_electrical_cap_fac = 44.0%<!-- 15,800 MWh/year / ( 4.1 MW * 365 days/year * 24h/day) = 0.440 --> | ps_annual_generation = 15.8 | ps_annual_gen_year = | website = | extra = }}
The '''Brandåa Hydroelectric Power Station''' ({{lang-no|Brandåa kraftverk}}) is a [[hydroelectricity|hydroelectric]] [[power station]] in the municipality of [[Rindal]] in [[Møre og Romsdal]] [[Counties of Norway|county]], [[Norway]]. It is a [[Run-of-the-river hydroelectricity|run-of-river hydro power station]] utilizing a drop of {{convert|373|m|sp=us}} in some tributaries of the [[Surna (Norway)|Surna River]].<ref name="Kvien"/> Permission was granted for construction in 2006<ref>[http://www.tk.no/nyheter/svorka-far-bygge-brandaa-kraftverk/s/1-113-2439891 Svorka får bygge Brandåa kraftverk. 2006. ''Tidens krav'' (November 29).]</ref> and the plant came into operation in 2009.<ref name="Kvien"/><ref name="Bk">[http://www.svorka.no/svorka-produksjon/produksjonsanlegg/brandaa-kraftverk Brandåa kraftverk] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150630222915/http://www.svorka.no/svorka-produksjon/produksjonsanlegg/brandaa-kraftverk |date=2015-06-30 }}</ref> It is operated by Svorka Produksjon AS.<ref name="Kvien"/> It operates at an installed capacity of {{nowrap|4.1 [[Megawatt|MW]]}},<ref name="Kvien"/> with an average annual production of about 15.8&nbsp;GWh.<ref name="Kvien"/><ref name="Bk"/>
