The '''Eolica Grădina Wind Farm''' is a proposed wind power project in [[Grădina]], [[Constanţa County]], [[Romania]]. It consists of two individual wind farms connected together. It will have 31 individual [[wind turbine]]s<ref>[http://www.edch.ch/projects/descriptions.shtml Eolica Dobrogea to build wind farm in the Dobrogea region] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090210014204/http://edch.ch/projects/descriptions.shtml |date=2009-02-10 }}</ref> with a nominal output of around 2 MW which will deliver up to 62 MW of power, enough to power over 41,000 homes, with a capital investment required of approximately US$75 million.

