{{About|commercial products with the name "Sunshower"|the meteorological phenomenon|Sunshower}}

Several commercial products share the name '''Sunshower'''.

Made by outdoors equipment producer [[Bear Stearns|Stearns Inc.]], the "Sun Shower" is an [[Thermal insulation|insulated]] bag that uses [[solar energy]] to heat water held within. Once heated, the user can take a shower, using the attached tubing and nozzle. Models vary, with different volumes, pressurizers, etc. Stearns also sells a variety of ''Sun Shower'' branded accessories, such as [[Biodegradable waste|bio-degradable]] soap and inflatable shower stalls.

In addition, [[Netherlands|Dutch]] company Sunshower B.V. makes a combination shower/[[tanning booth]] branded ''The Sunshower''.

